sequenceDiagram
    participant ESP32
    participant HiveMQ
    participant Backend
    participant Supabase
    participant Flutter

    ESP32->>HiveMQ: Publish flow readings
    HiveMQ->>Backend: MQTT message received
    Backend->>Backend: Validate + detect leak
    Backend->>Supabase: Batch insert readings
    Flutter->>Backend: Request analytics
    Backend->>Supabase: Query summaries
    Backend-->>Flutter: Return JSON data
